### Enrichment
Zettelkasten community continues active discussion on zettelkasten.de forum. The 2026 Readlistic guide to Zettelkasten for readers emphasizes the maturity model (fleeting -> literature -> permanent). Structure notes and keywords are emerging as additional note types beyond the classic three. The beestgraph implementation with GRADUATED_FROM and SPARKED_BY graph edges is a novel enhancement that the community would find interesting. Consider publishing the graph-enhanced Zettelkasten approach.

